<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Apache Deployment Report</title>

```
<style>
    body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }

    .header {
        background: #d9480f;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .content {
        padding: 25px;
    }

    .success {
        background: #ebfbee;
        color: #2b8a3e;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    .failed {
        background: #fff5f5;
        color: #c92a2a;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline-block;
    }

    table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    table th {
        background: #f1f3f5;
        text-align: left;
        padding: 10px;
    }

    table td {
        padding: 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
    }

    .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #868e96;
        background: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
    }

    .button {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        background: #d9480f;
        color: white !important;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>
```

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

```
<div class="header">
    <h1>Apache HTTPD Deployment Report</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">

    {% if deployment_status == 'Already_Deployed' %}

        <span class="success">SUCCESS</span>

        <p>Hello Team,</p>

        <p>
            Apache HTTPD service is already installed and running on the target server.
            No deployment action was required.
        </p>

    {% elif deployment_status == 'Successfully_Deployed' %}

        <span class="success">SUCCESS</span>

        <p>Hello Team,</p>

        <p>
            Apache HTTPD service has been successfully deployed and started on the target server.
        </p>

    {% else %}

        <span class="failed">FAILED</span>

        <p>Hello Team,</p>

        <p>
            Apache deployment failed. Please review the Ansible execution logs for details.
        </p>

    {% endif %}

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th colspan="2">Deployment Details</th>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>Target Host</strong></td>
            <td>{{ inventory_hostname }}</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>IP Address</strong></td>
            <td>{{ ansible_default_ipv4.address | default('N/A') }}</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>Operating System</strong></td>
            <td>{{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>Service Name</strong></td>
            <td>httpd.service</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>Deployment Status</strong></td>
            <td>{{ deployment_status }}</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>Execution Time</strong></td>
            <td>{{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td><strong>Environment</strong></td>
            <td>{{ env_name | default('Production') }}</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    {% if deployment_status != 'Failed' %}
    <center>
        <a href="http://{{ ansible_host | default(inventory_hostname) }}"
           class="button">
            Verify Apache Website
        </a>
    </center>
    {% endif %}

</div>

<div class="footer">
    This is an automated notification generated by Ansible Automation.
</div>
```

</div>

</body>
</html>
